title: Movimento do Porto
body:
In the period from 1901 to 1943, the following number of vessels entered the port of Funchal:

| Year | Number of vessels |
|------|-------------------|
| 1901 | 1,168             |
| 1902 | 1,564             |
| 1903 | 1,394             |
| 1904 | 1,301             |
| 1905 | 1,318             |
| ...  | ...               |
